<text><body>
<lb n="0739a05"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0739a06"/>
<lb n="0739a07"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0739001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此經明本也以宋本元本宮本知本對校，〔佛說…經〕六字－【知】</note><app n="0739001" word-count="6"><lem><title>佛說時非時經</title></lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0739001" place="foot" type="rest">此經明本也以宋本元本宮本知本對校</note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0739a08"/>
<lb n="0739a09"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0739002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天竺三藏＝外國【宮】，〔天竺…譯〕十字－【知】</note><note n="0739002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔天竺三藏法師若羅嚴譯〕十字－【知】，天竺三藏＝外國【宮】</note><app n="0739002"><lem>天竺三藏法師若羅嚴譯</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">外國法師若羅嚴譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0739a10"/><div1 type="jing"><p>如是我聞。一時佛住王舍城迦蘭陀竹<note n="0739003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔林〕－【知】</note><app n="0739003"><lem>林</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0739a11"/>園精舍。<note n="0739004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（是）＋時【知】</note><app n="0739004"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">是時</rdg></app>佛告諸比丘。我當為汝說時
<lb n="0739a12"/><note n="0739005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（與）＋非【知】</note><app n="0739005"><lem>非</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">與非</rdg></app>時經。善思<note n="0739006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念之＝憶念【知】</note><app n="0739006"><lem>念之</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">憶念</rdg></app>。諸比丘言。<note n="0739007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔如是〕－【宮】</note><app n="0739007"><lem>如是</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>世
<lb n="0739a13"/>尊。<note n="0739008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝謹【知】</note><app n="0739008"><lem>當</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">謹</rdg></app>受教聽。佛告諸比丘。是中何者為
<lb n="0739a14"/>時。何者為非時。比丘當知</p>
<lb n="0739a15"/><p>冬初<note n="0739009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔分〕－【知】＊</note><app n="0739009"><lem>分</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0739a16"/><p><note n="0739010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔第一〕－【知】＊</note><app n="0739010"><lem>第一</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>十五日七&CB00560;為時。四&CB00560;半<note n="0739011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（為）＋非時【知】下同</note><app n="0739011"><lem>非時</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">為非時</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0739a17"/><p><note n="0739012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔從…日〕十字－【知】，以下知恩院本非時下總無從乃至　等期日</note><app n="0739012" word-count="10"><lem>從八月十六日至三十日</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0739012" place="foot" type="rest">以下知恩院本非時下總無從乃至　等期日</note></p>
<lb n="0739a18"/><p>第二十五日。八&CB00560;為時。六&CB00560;八指非時</p>
<lb n="0739a19"/><p>從九月一日至十五日</p>
<lb n="0739a20"/><p>第三十五日。九&CB00560;為時。七&CB00560;六指非時</p>
<lb n="0739a21"/><p>從九月十六日至三十日</p>
<lb n="0739a22"/><p>第四十五日。十&CB00560;為時。八&CB00560;三指非時</p>
<lb n="0739a23"/><p>從十月一日至十五日</p>
<lb n="0739a24"/><p>第五十五日。十一&CB00560;為時。九&CB00560;<note n="0739013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔四指〕－【知】</note><app n="0739013"><lem>四指</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>非時</p>
<lb n="0739a25"/><p>從十月十六日至三十日</p>
<lb n="0739a26"/><p>第六十五日。十二&CB00560;為時。十一&CB00560;六指非
<lb n="0739a27"/>時</p><p type="inline">從十一月一日至十五日</p>
<lb n="0739a28"/><p>第七十五日。十一&CB00560;半為時。十&CB00560;三指非
<lb n="0739a29"/>時</p><p type="inline">從十一月十六日至三十日</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0794b.0739b" n="0739b"/>
<lb n="0739b01"/><p>第八十五日。十一&CB00560;為時。九&CB00560;四指非<note n="0739014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＋（冬四月竟）夾註【知】</note><app n="0739014"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">時<note place="inline">冬四月竟</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0739b02"/><p>從十二月一日至十五日</p>
<lb n="0739b03"/><p>春初<anchor id="fxT17p0739b01"/>分</p>
<lb n="0739b04"/><p><anchor id="fxT17p0739b02"/>第一十五日。十&CB00560;為時。八&CB00560;<note n="0739015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔少〕－【知】</note><app n="0739015"><lem>少</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>三指非時</p>
<lb n="0739b05"/><p>從十二月十六日至三十日</p>
<lb n="0739b06"/><p>第二十五日。九&CB00560;半為時。七&CB00560;少三指非
<lb n="0739b07"/>時</p><p type="inline">從正月一日至十五日</p>
<lb n="0739b08"/><p>第三十五日。九&CB00560;為時。六&CB00560;少三指非時</p>
<lb n="0739b09"/><p>從正月十六日至三十日</p>
<lb n="0739b10"/><p>第四十五日。八&CB00560;為時。五&CB00560;<note n="0739016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔少三指〕－【知】</note><app n="0739016"><lem>少三指</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>非時</p>
<lb n="0739b11"/><p>從二月一日至十五日</p>
<lb n="0739b12"/><p>第五十五日。七&CB00560;為時。<note n="0739017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝四【知】</note><app n="0739017"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">四</rdg></app>&CB00560;少三指非時</p>
<lb n="0739b13"/><p>從二月十六日至三十日</p>
<lb n="0739b14"/><p>第六十五日。六&CB00560;為時。三&CB00560;少四指非時</p>
<lb n="0739b15"/><p>從三月一日至十五日</p>
<lb n="0739b16"/><p>第七十五日。五&CB00560;為時。三&CB00560;少三指非時</p>
<lb n="0739b17"/><p>從三月十六日至三十日</p>
<lb n="0739b18"/><p>第八十五日。四&CB00560;為時。二&CB00560;少一指非<note n="0739018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＋（春四月竟）夾註【知】</note><app n="0739018"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">時<note place="inline">春四月竟</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0739b19"/><p>從四月一日至十五日</p>
<lb n="0739b20"/><p>夏初<anchor id="fxT17p0739b03"/>分</p>
<lb n="0739b21"/><p><anchor id="fxT17p0739b04"/>第一十五日。三&CB00560;為時。二&CB00560;少四指非時</p>
<lb n="0739b22"/><p>從四月十六日至三十日</p>
<lb n="0739b23"/><p>第二十五日。二&CB00560;為時。一&CB00560;少五指非時</p>
<lb n="0739b24"/><p>從五月一日至十五日</p>
<lb n="0739b25"/><p>第三十五日。二&CB00560;半為時。一&CB00560;<note n="0739019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">少三指＝半【知】</note><app n="0739019"><lem>少三指</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">半</rdg></app>非
<lb n="0739b26"/>時</p><p type="inline">從五月十六日至三十日</p>
<lb n="0739b27"/><p>第四十五日。三&CB00560;半為時。二&CB00560;少二指非
<lb n="0739b28"/>時</p><p type="inline">從六月一日至十五日</p>
<lb n="0739b29"/><p>第五十五日。四&CB00560;半為時。二&CB00560;半非時</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0794b.0739c" n="0739c"/>
<lb n="0739c01"/><p>從六月十六日至三十日</p>
<lb n="0739c02"/><p>第六十五日。五&CB00560;為時。三&CB00560;非時</p><p type="inline">從七
<lb n="0739c03"/>月一日至十五日</p>
<lb n="0739c04"/><p>第七十五日。五&CB00560;半為時。三&CB00560;半非時</p>
<lb n="0739c05"/><p>從七月十<note n="0739020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">六＝五【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0739020"><lem>六</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">五</rdg></app>日至三十日</p>
<lb n="0739c06"/><p>第八十五日。六&CB00560;為時。四&CB00560;<note n="0739021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔半〕－【知】</note><app n="0739021"><lem>半</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>非<note n="0739022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＋（夏四月竟）夾註【知】</note><app n="0739022"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">時<note place="inline">夏四月竟</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0739c07"/><p>從八月一日至十五日</p>
<lb n="0739c08"/><p>如是諸比丘。我已說十二月時非時。為諸
<lb n="0739c09"/>聲聞<note n="0739023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【知】</note><app n="0739023"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>所應<note n="0739024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝作【知】</note><app n="0739024"><lem>行</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">作</rdg></app>。憐愍利益故說。我所應
<lb n="0739c10"/><note n="0739025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔作〕－【知】</note><app n="0739025"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><anchor id="fxT17p0739c01"/>已竟。汝等當行。若樹<note n="0739026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＝下【宮】</note><app n="0739026"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">下</rdg></app>空處。露坐
<lb n="0739c11"/>思惟。諸比丘莫為放逸後致悔恨。是我所
<lb n="0739c12"/>教戒。佛說<note n="0739027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經竟＝是法【知】</note><app n="0739027"><lem>經竟</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">是法</rdg></app>。時諸比丘。皆大歡喜。<note n="0739028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔勸助〕－【知】</note><app n="0739028"><lem>勸
<lb n="0739c13"/>助</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0739029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受持＝奉行【知】</note><app n="0739029"><lem>受持</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">奉行</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0739c14"/><trailer>佛說時非時經</trailer><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
<lb n="0739c15"/><div1 type="W"><lg><l>因緣輕慢故</l><l>命終墮<note n="0739030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">地獄＝惡道【知】</note><app n="0739030"><lem>地獄</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">惡道</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0739c16"/><l>因緣修善者</l><l>於此生天上</l>
<lb n="0739c17"/><l>緣斯修善業</l><l>離惡得解脫</l>
<lb n="0739c18"/><l>不善<note n="0739031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＝觀【知】</note><app n="0739031"><lem>欲</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">觀</rdg></app>因緣</l><l>身壞入惡道</l></lg>
<lb n="0739c19"/><p><note n="0739032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天竺三藏＝外國【宮】，〔天竺…訖〕二十七字－【知】</note><note n="0739032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔天竺三藏法師若羅嚴手執梵本口自宣譯涼州道人于闐城中寫訖〕二十七字－【知】，天竺三藏＝外國【宮】</note><app n="0739032"><lem>天竺三藏法師若羅嚴。手執<note n="0739033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">梵＝胡【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0739033"><lem>梵</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">胡</rdg></app>本。口自
<lb n="0739c20"/>宣譯。涼州道人。<note n="0739034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">于闐＝釬&CB07018;【宮】</note><app n="0739034"><lem>于闐</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">釬&CB07018;</rdg></app>城中寫訖</lem><rdg wit="【知】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">外國法師若羅嚴手執梵本口自宣譯涼州道人于闐城中寫訖</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0739c21"/><lg><l>披褐懷玉</l><l>深智作愚</l><l>外如夷人</l>
<lb n="0739c22"/><l>內懷明珠</l><l>千億萬劫</l><l>與道同軀<note n="0739035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下知恩院本有經題並光明皇后願文</note></l></lg></div1></body></text></TEI.2>
